1. *Bebe* su obožavale da se igraju u parku. (Babies liked to play in the park.)
2. Oni su za *bebu* kupili novu igračku. (They bought a new toy for the baby.)
3. Mogu li *bebe* da uče da plivaju? (Can babies learn to swim?)
4. Moj sestrić je bio *bebu* sa crvenim šeširom. (My nephew was a baby with a red hat.)
5. Oni su za *bebu* uveli nove navike. (They introduced new habits for the baby.)